Package org.dspace.app.dav

Class Summary
DAVServlet Servlet implementing WebDAV server for DSpace.
LNISoapServlet Servlet implementing SOAP services of DSpace Lightweight Network Interface
LoadDSpaceLNIConfig Deprecated. Use Servlet Context Listener provided in dspace-api (remove in > 1.5.x)
 

Exception Summary
DAVStatusException Encapsulate the components of an HTTP status response, namely an integer code and a text message.
LNIRemoteException Container for all exceptions thrown by DSpace LNI SOAP methods.
